{"tid":840480,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我好開心","createTime":"2018-09-28T19:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T03:54:28.000Z","uid":89783,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"148b7d3d197c8ad4b040aafd18c96d8fc95f3519","tid":840480,"uid":89783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T19:57:20.000Z","msg":"唔知幾時開始自己好負面情緒，但當你發現最好的朋友都接受唔到自己呢一面，其實佢聽我呻下已經好開心。我覺得自己好似比緊壓力人地。然後我發現我扮開心，有時扮到自已都呃埋，我係咪就黎痴線。我愈正面樂觀我就愈不安，你話我可以點。無人明好慘。<br />\n<br />\n我啲朋友都好好，只係我自己太垃圾。我已經好努力好積極，但我好似呃緊自己。"},{"pid":"0f63d84ef4b1bb6f739ee415f4d04da62e169766","tid":840480,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T20:12:27.000Z","msg":"搵啲陌生人講"},{"pid":"cf16b40e75a8cf34cb83a27f10573099d0dc66cd","tid":840480,"uid":142247,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T20:17:22.000Z","msg":"屌我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身個人日日放負<br />\n成日搵fd開解又覺得麻煩到佢地<br />\n而家開始改變緊心態<br />\n因為真係有目標想達成<br />\n但唔知係咪自己呃緊自己<br />\n因為如果有機會可以死撚咗佢<br />\n就死咗佢算<br />\n<br />\n以前對住人會嘻皮笑臉唔想人知自己諗法原來咁抑鬱<br />\n而家好似連自己都呃埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d747fe319534e154fadd9327d4cca3a7d4bb3f4","tid":840480,"uid":89783,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0f63d84ef4b1bb6f739ee415f4d04da62e169766","tid":840480,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T20:12:27.000Z","msg":"搵啲陌生人講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T20:24:26.000Z","msg":"嗨你"},{"pid":"675cb915bdeac1aab54925aa74b82f5e33134290","tid":840480,"uid":36402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4d747fe319534e154fadd9327d4cca3a7d4bb3f4","tid":840480,"uid":89783,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0f63d84ef4b1bb6f739ee415f4d04da62e169766","tid":840480,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T20:12:27.000Z","msg":"搵啲陌生人講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T20:24:26.000Z","msg":"嗨你"},"cited